Linear Regression Example

jdt

11/26/2020

Generate the Simulated Data

set.seed(123)
n=30         #sample size
beta_0=10    #true y-intercept
beta_1=2    #true slope
sigma= 9     #true sigma

x=25*runif(n)
y=beta_0 + beta_1*x + sigma*rnorm(n)

Graph of data

plot(y~x)
abline(lm(y~x))

Results

result<-lm(y~x)
summary(result)
